    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふう、今日はこれくらいにしておくか\n……ん？　奥山さんからの電話？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ I guess I'll call it a day for now…\n…Huh? A phone call from Okuyama-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん。今お電話大丈夫でしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san. Are you free?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、大丈夫だよ。今日もお疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Good job today too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんもお疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san! Good job to you too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "遅刻しかけた時はどうなるかと思いましたけど……\nさとみさんのおかげでなんとかなりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was really worried when I almost arrived late…\nBut thanks to Satomi-san‚ I managed somehow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、現場についてしばらくは\n視界がぐらぐらしてたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ when I first arrived at the location‚\nmy vision was a bit shaky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの運転は独特だからな……\n俺も番組のスタッフさんに心配されたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hashimoto-san has a unique driving style…\nEven the staff on the show were worried about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "今日は本当にすみませんでした……\nまさかお財布も携帯も台本も全部忘れるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really sorry about today…\nI can't believe I forgot my wallet‚ phone‚ and script.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4648582458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないでいいよ。今日はゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. Just rest well today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6648582458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.3981915791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ありがとうございます\nそれじゃあ、お休みなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… Thank you very much.\nWell then‚ good night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1648582458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 69.0315249125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……奥山さんがあんな忘れ物をするとはな\n一刻も早く悩みを解決してあげないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can't believe Okuyama-san forgot such important things.\nI need to solve her problem as soon as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8981915791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4981915791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 79.6648582458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん。定期テストまでの仕事のスケジュールを\n調整してみたんだ。ちょっと確認してくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ I adjusted the schedule for your work\nuntil the midterm exams. Can you take a look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6981915791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood… Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2981915791,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 87.2981915791
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "空き時間が増えてるんですけど……\nもしかしてお仕事を減らしちゃったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like I have more free time…\nDid you reduce my work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、違う。よく見たら仕事終わりが早くなってたり\n微妙な隙間時間がなくなったりしてる……凄いです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ no. If I look closely‚ the end times of the jobs are earlier‚\nand there are no small gaps in between… This is amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "先方と調整して、少しでも奥山さんの勉強時間を\n確保するようにしたんだ。どうだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I coordinated with the other side to secure more study time for you.\nHow does it look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nこれならなんとかなりそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nWith this‚ I think I'll manage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "……私、定期テスト最終日にある撮影が\nここ最近のお仕事の中でも一番楽しみだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Among the recent jobs‚ the one I'm most excited about is\nthe shoot on the final day of the midterm exams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "その日の撮影って言うと……\n野外音楽堂がある自然公園のPR動画だったか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that the PR video\nfor the natural park with the outdoor music hall?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6981915791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n一面に広がるお花畑が本っ当に綺麗なんですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nThe flower field that spreads out is really beautiful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "それにそれに！　撮影で着る予定のドレスが\nとっっっても可愛いんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ and! The dress I'm going to wear\nfor the shoot is soooo cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなので……撮影前のテストが\nぼろぼろになっちゃうのは絶対避けたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why… I really want to avoid having the tests\nright before the shoot and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2648582458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "「テスト、全然ダメだったなぁ」なんて思ってたら\n引きずっちゃいますしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "feeling like \"I did terrible on the exams.\"\nIt would drag me down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.4648582458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "なので、このスケジュールの調整、本当に助かります\nありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this schedule adjustment is really helpful.\nThank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "定期テストまで、ばっちり勉強するぞー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll study hard until the midterm exams!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.0315249125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
